= content_for :navbar_class, "navbar-absolute"

%header(id="promo#{Time.current.year}" class="hero")
  %div(class="hero-background")
    = image_tag asset_path('hero/home-hero.jpg'), loading: "lazy"
  %div(class="content")
    %div(class="hero-container hero-container-high")
      %div(class="hero-header")
        %div(class="hero-header-title")
          %h1(class="text text-xxxl text-medium hero-title") Making wholesale better, together.
        %div(class="hero-header-caption")
          %p(class="text text-xxl hero-caption") Dagglo dreams of making wholesale for a more simple and transparent.
        %div(class="hero-header-actions")
          %div(class="hero-header-actions-item")
            = link_to "Sign up to sell", new_seller_path, class: "button"
          %div(class="hero-header-actions-item")
            = link_to "Learn more about selling", "", class: "link"



%section(class="section section-page")
  %div(class="content")
    %div(class="header header-center")
      %h1(class="text text-xl text-medium") We are taking wholesale in a new direction. With advanced technology, transparency, and more opportunities, both buyers and sellers win.

    %div(class="section-page-block")
      %div(class="grid-1-3")
        %div(class="col")
          %div(class="testimonial")
            %div(class="testimonial-container")
              %div(class="testimonial-icon")
                = icon "far", "circle-notch"
              %div(class="testimonial-header")
                %h1(class="text text-m text-medium") Transparency
              %div(class="testimonial-body")
                %p(class="text text-s text-secondary") With clear, upfront pricing and unrivaled visibility, you always have the information needed to make the right business decisions.

        %div(class="col")
          %div(class="testimonial")
            %div(class="testimonial-container")
              %div(class="testimonial-icon")
                = icon "far", "hand-point-up"
              %div(class="testimonial-header")
                %h1(class="text text-m text-medium") Wholesale at your fingertips
              %div(class="testimonial-body")
                %p(class="text text-s text-secondary") Our streamlined workflow and 24/7 support keeps your business rolling, quickly, and efficiently.

        %div(class="col")
          %div(class="testimonial")
            %div(class="testimonial-container")
              %div(class="testimonial-icon")
                = icon "far", "rocket-launch"
              %div(class="testimonial-header")
                %h1(class="text text-m text-medium") The Uber of freight
              %div(class="testimonial-body")
                %p(class="text text-s text-secondary") Uber technology has revolutionized the way people move. Now, weâ€™re doing the same for the freight industry.


